v0.1.3    2022-06-29 17:16:15+01:00 Europe/London
  [Enhancements]
  - The nonce is combined with the PID to ensure it is unique after forking.

  [Documentation]
  - Added HTTP::SecureHeaders and Plack::Middleware::CSP to SEE ALSO.

  [Toolchain]
  - Sign release.

